Ayo maju.

25
00:04:36.980 --> 00:04:40.850
Rupanya kau kesulitan
melenyapkan rasa benci.

26
00:04:43.230 --> 00:04:44.020
Siapa kau?

27
00:04:45.220 --> 00:04:46.190
Di bawah sembilan langit,

28
00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:49.650
di atas sembilan bumi,

29
00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:53.650
dengan diberkati bulu hitam,

30
00:04:55.110 --> 00:04:57.310
aku dilahirkan dengan tumpukan kebencian.

31
00:04:59.310 --> 00:05:01.230
Namaku 'Jiuyou'.
